Dialogue: 100,0:00:05.98,0:00:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kobayashi's Dragon Something!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:08.94,0:00:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with the "something"?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:10.69,0:00:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Please insert a word that ends with a "D."
Dialogue: 100,0:00:13.99,0:00:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Just like how "Maid" plus "Dragon" makes "Maidragon."
Dialogue: 100,0:00:17.33,0:00:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do we have to do something so random?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:19.70,0:00:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a project.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:20.75,0:00:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A project?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:21.70,0:00:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to create some extras.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:24.58,0:00:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Something to differentiate the BDs \Nfrom the broadcast episodes.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:28.38,0:00:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to dignity?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:30.21,0:00:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's get started!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:32.72,0:00:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Band.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:33.84,0:00:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\t(27,236,\c&HFFFFFF&)}Miss Kobayashi's Bandragon!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:40.97,0:00:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all over the place.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:42.35,0:00:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is my attire so plain?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:44.60,0:00:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The important thing is what we play.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:46.48,0:00:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's think of a direction to go with the music.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:48.86,0:00:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Then do the costumes even matter?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:50.94,0:00:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yodeling.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:51.90,0:00:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Who wants that?{Is there any demand?}
Dialogue: 100,0:00:52.94,0:00:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Idol!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:53.78,0:00:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not a band...
Dialogue: 100,0:00:55.03,0:00:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Enka!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:55.91,0:00:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Due to creative differences, we're disbanding.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:58.53,0:01:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't even made our debut!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:00.54,0:01:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Mermaid.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:01.66,0:01:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\t(27,235,\c&HFFFFFF&)}Miss Kobayashi's Mermaidragon!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:04.66,0:01:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We're mermaids.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:05.87,0:01:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're backwards.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:06.87,0:01:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kobayashi, you're my prince!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:08.63,0:01:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, you have it backward!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:10.30,0:01:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's dance!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:11.38,0:01:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's completely unrelated.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:13.17,0:01:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Here is a gift.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:13.97,0:01:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a dud, isn't it?{???}
Dialogue: 100,0:01:16.88,0:01:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Can't breathe!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:18.43,0:01:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You breathe through gills?!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:20.14,0:01:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,India.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:21.35,0:01:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kobayashi's Indragon!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:23.81,0:01:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The "India = curry" idea is pretty weak.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:27.15,0:01:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Namaste.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:28.86,0:01:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Iceland.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:30.48,0:01:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kobayashi's Icelandragon!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:32.94,0:01:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Too literal.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:34.36,0:01:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,New Zealand.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:35.74,0:01:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kobayashi's New Zealandragon!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:38.20,0:01:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough geography.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:39.78,0:01:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Avocado.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:41.37,0:01:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kobayashi's Avocadragon!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:43.70,0:01:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like it sounds, huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:45.33,0:01:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You split?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:46.29,0:01:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Do-re-mi-fa-so-la-ti-do.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:48.54,0:01:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kobayashi's Do-re-mi-fa-so-la-ti-dragon!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:51.67,0:01:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of ideas, huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:53.25,0:01:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Nude.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:54.51,0:01:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kobayashi's Nudragon!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:56.88,0:01:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're under arrest.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:58.51,0:02:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, we'll fill in the blank space again,
Dialogue: 100,0:02:02.10,0:02:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,with {\i1}Miss Kobayashi's Dragon Something{\i0}!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:04.85,0:02:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,To be continued!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:05.68,0:02:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We're making more?!
Comment: 100,0:00:05.98,0:00:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kobayashi's Dragon {\fscx750}_{\fscx}!